Interface ContentVersionDocumentType.ContentVersionFields

  • Enclosing class:
    ContentVersionDocumentType

    public static interface ContentVersionDocumentType.ContentVersionFields
    Reflects the fields of a ContentVersion object.
    Since:
    8.1.0
    Version:
    $Revision: 17592 $ $Date: 2015-07-17 11:19:32 -0300 (Fri, 17 Jul 2015) $

    • Field Summary

      Fields 
      Modifier and Type Field and Description
      static DocumentTypeField ACTIVE_VERSION
      Boolean field that indicates that this version is set as a ContentLocale.getActiveVersion().
      static CompositeDocumentTypeField CONTENT_LOCALE
      Field that corresponds to the ContentLocale object returned by ContentVersion.getContentLocale().
      static CompositeDocumentTypeField CONTENT_VERSION
      Field that corresponds to a ContentVersion object.

      Field that corresponds to ContentVersion.getId().

      Field that corresponds to ContentVersion.getLastModifiedDateTime().
      static DocumentTypeField PRIMARY_NAME
      Field that corresponds to ContentVersion.getPrimaryName().
      static CompositeDocumentTypeField PUBLICATIONS
      Field that corresponds to the list of ContentPublication objects returned by ContentVersion.getPublications().
      static DocumentTypeField PUBLISHED_VERSION
      Boolean field that indicates that this version is set as a ContentLocale.getPublishedVersion().
      static DocumentTypeField VERSION_NUMBER
      Field that corresponds to ContentVersion.getVersionNumber().
